<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Empoison" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Empoison,</orth> to destroy: <cit><quote>how much an ill word may e. liking,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 3.1.86" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 1, 86</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a man by his own alms --ed, and with his charity slain,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 5.6.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 6, 11</bibl></cit> (cf. <emph>Poison</emph>).
